4e6.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcjmm429jj4ro%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Germans%20-%20divided%20by%20politics%20and%20economic%20struggles%20-%20hope%20to%20unite%20behind%20the%20national%20side.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcjmm429jj4ro%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22War%20Of%20Words%20Between%20BJP%2C%20Maharashtra%20Ally%20Over%20Article%20By%20RSS%20Leader%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20its%20ally%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%2C%20seem%20to%20have%20hit%20a%20rocky%20road%20after%20their%20rivals%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20won%20more%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20two%20parties%20on%20Thursday%20engaged%20in%20a%20war%20of%20words%20over%20an%20article%20in%20Organiser%2C%20a%20weekly%20known%20to%20be%20close%20to%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh.%20The%20article%20had%20criticised%20the%20BJP%20for%20contesting%20the%20elections%20along%20with%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%20won%2030%20seats%20in%20the%20recently%20held%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20The%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20won%2017%2C%20of%20which%20NCP%20scored%20only%20one.%20Maharashtra%20sends%20second-highest%20representatives%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20-%2048%20-%20only%20next%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%2080.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20launched%20an%20internal%20survey%20to%20assess%20if%20they%20should%20contest%20alone%20in%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20to%20be%20held%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20article%2C%20a%20senior%20RSS%20leader%20questioned%20the%20BJP's%20move%20to%20enter%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20NCP%2C%20terming%20the%20move%20%26quot%3Bill-advised%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20was%20this%20ill-advised%20step%20taken%3F%20BJP%20supporters%20were%20hurt%20because%20they%20had%20fought%20against%20this%20Congress%20ideology%20for%20years%20and%20were%20persecuted.%20In%20a%20single%20stroke%2C%20BJP%20reduced%20its%20brand%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20RSS'%20Ratan%20Sharda%20wrote%20in%20the%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaharashtra%20is%20a%20prime%20example%20of%20unnecessary%20politicking%20and%20avoidable%20manipulations.%20Well-performing%20parliamentarians%20were%20ignored%20to%20accommodate%20such%20late%20comers%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20senior%20NCP%20leader%20Praful%20Patel%20though%20said%20that%20the%20article%20shouldn't%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20sign%20that%20all%20is%20not%20well%20between%20the%20two%20allies.%20%26quot%3BAn%20article%20in%20a%20weekly%20does%20not%20reflect%20the%20BJP's%20stance.%20It%20should%20not%20be%20interpreted%20in%20that%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20NCP%20youth%20wing%20leader%20Sooraj%20Chavan%20lashed%20out%20saying%20that%20when%20the%20BJP%20performs%20well%2C%20credit%20is%20given%20to%20the%20hard%20work%20of%20the%20RSS%20but%20a%20defeat%20is%20blamed%20on%20Ajit%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%2C%20BJP%20leader%20Pravin%20Darekar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20RSS%20is%20like%20a%20father%20figure%20to%20all%20of%20us.%20There%20is%20no%20need%20to%20make%20comments%20about%20the%20RSS.%20Sooraj%20Chavan%20should%20not%20have%20rushed%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20organisation.%20The%20BJP%20has%20not%20commented%20against%20the%20NCP.%20It%20would%20be%20better%20if%20such%20issues%20are%20discussed%20during%20NDA%20meetings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20signs%20of%20discord%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20emerged%20when%20the%20NCP%20denied%20a%20Minister%20of%20State%20post%20in%20the%20new%20government%2C%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20Praful%20Patel%20both%20expressed%20a%20desire%20for%20a%20cabinet%20berth%20while%20rejecting%20the%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20argument%20from%20the%20NCP's%20side%20is%20that%20Mr%20Patel%2C%20as%20a%20former%20cabinet%20minister%2C%20is%20too%20senior%20a%20figure%20to%20hold%20a%20junior%20minister's%20post.%20Ajit%20Pawar%20told%20reporters%20his%20party%20is%20%26quot%3Bready%20to%20wait%26quot%3B%20for%20that%20cabinet%20berth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patel%20was%20similarly%20resolute%2C%20telling%20reporters%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20earlier%20cabinet%20minister%20(in%20the%20Congress-led%20UPA%20government%20and%20being%20made%20MoS%20(Minister%20of%20State)%20is%20a%20demotion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20NCP%2C%20part%20of%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20in%20Maharashtra%20along%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20managed%20to%20win%20just%20one%20seat%20(Raigad)%20of%20the%20four%20it%20contested%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20It%20also%20lost%20the%20prestige%20battle%20in%20Baramati%2C%20where%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20wife%20Sunetra%20Pawar%20was%20trounced%20by%20the%20sitting%20MP%20from%20the%20rival%20NCP%20faction%20and%20his%20cousin%2C%20Supriya%20Sule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indo-Asian%20News%20Service%2C%20citing%20unnamed%20sources%2C%20reported%20that%20after%20the%20results%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20considering%20whether%20to%20continue%20the%20alliance%20with%20Ajit%20Pawar%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20surveys%20have%20been%20launched%20to%20find%20out%20how%20the%20party%20will%20get%20the%20simple%20majority%20going%20solo.%20Besides%2C%20the%20surveys%20will%20also%20show%20how%20the%20BJP%20will%20perform%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena.%20It%20will%20also%20gauge%20the%20mood%20about%20whether%20to%20continue%20its%20alliance%20with%20the%20NCP%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20BJP%20source%20told%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%20score%20this%20time%2C%20240%2C%20was%20much%20lower%20than%20its%202019%20tally%20of%20303%20and%20the%20282%20seats%20it%20won%20in%202014.%20The%20Congress%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20registered%20a%20strong%20growth%2C%20winning%2099%20seats%20compared%20to%2052%20it%20won%20in%202019%20and%2044%20seats%20in%202014.%20The%20INDIA%20bloc%20crossed%20the%20230%20mark%2C%20posing%20stiff%20competition%2C%20and%20defying%20all%20predictions%20from%20exit%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718340420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fe913t30g_ajit-pawar-devendra-fadnavis-eknath-shinde-pti_625x300_05_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-vs-ajit-pawar-ncp-over-article-questioning-alliance-in-maharashtra-5886791%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20and%20its%20ally%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%2C%20seem%20to%20have%20hit%20a%20rocky%20road%20after%20their%20rivals%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20won%20more%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-vs-ajit-pawar-ncp-over-article-questioning-alliance-in-maharashtra-5886791%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20says%202%20military%20employees%20sold%2060%20pounds%20of%20secret%20documents%20to%20a%20recycling%20plant%2C%20allowing%20a%20shopper%20to%20bag%204%20volumes%20for%20under%20%241%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222766%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chinese%20paramilitary%20police%20border%20guards%20train%20in%20the%20snow%20at%20Mohe%20County%20in%20China's%20northeast%20Heilongjiang%20province%2C%20on%20the%20border%20with%20Russia%2C%20on%20December%2012%2C%202016.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666bc3cf764df1611259ce9e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221825%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChinese%20paramilitary%20police%20border%20guards%20train%20in%20the%20snow%20at%20Mohe%20County%20in%20China's%20northeast%20Heilongjiang%20province%2C%20on%20the%20border%20with%20Russia%2C%20on%20December%2012%2C%202016.%3Cp%3ESTR%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChina%20on%20Thursday%20highlighted%20an%20intelligence%20gaffe%20involving%20200%20sensitive%20military%20documents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20said%20two%20military%20personnel%20who%20were%20supposed%20to%20destroy%20the%20documents%20sold%20them%20for%20under%20%244.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20retiree%20bought%20four%20volumes%20of%20the%20secrets%20for%20about%20%240.85%20from%20a%20recycling%20plant%2C%20authorities%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20State%20Security%20Ministry%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20a%20retiree%20had%20somehow%20secured%20four%20volumes%20of%20confidential%20military%20documents%20at%20a%20recycling%20store%20for%20just%2085%20cents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20described%20the%20incident%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2FQD8MOVukB7gHlQ3p2qnZaQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%20post%20%3C%2Fa%3Eencouraging%20the%20public%20to%20be%20vigilant%20on%20national%20security%20matters%2C%20and%20praised%20the%20retiree%20for%20reporting%20the%20documents%20to%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20identified%20as%20%26quot%3BGrandpa%20Zhang.%26quot%3B%20Chinese%20authorities%20and%20media%20typically%20do%20not%20publish%20the%20full%20names%20of%20people%20who%20don't%20have%20a%20high%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20post%2C%20Zhang%20is%20a%20former%20employee%20of%20a%20state-owned%20enterprise%20and%20collects%20military%20newspapers%20and%20magazines%20as%20a%20hobby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20walking%20in%20his%20neighborhood%20when%20he%20passed%20a%20scrap