rs%20and%20proxy%20firms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnstage%20at%20the%20annual%20shareholder%20meeting%20in%20Austin%2C%20Texas%2C%20Musk%20described%20himself%20as%20pathologically%20optimistic.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20wasn't%20optimistic%20this%20wouldn't%20exist%2C%20this%20factory%20wouldn't%20exist%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20to%20applause.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20do%20deliver%20in%20the%20end.%20That's%20the%20important%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20tipped%20off%20late%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20the%20proposals%20were%20garnering%20huge%20support.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20approval%20does%20not%2C%20however%2C%20resolve%20a%20lawsuit%20on%20the%20pay%20package%20in%20a%20Delaware%20court%2C%20which%20some%20legal%20experts%20think%20could%20stretch%20out%20for%20months.%20The%20judge%20invalidated%20the%20pay%20package%20in%20January%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bunfathomable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20may%20also%20face%20fresh%20lawsuits%20on%20the%20package%2C%20which%20would%20be%20the%20largest%20in%20U.S.%20corporate%20history.%20Shareholders%20had%20voted%20for%20this%20package%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20thing%20is%20not%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Brian%20Quinn%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20Boston%20College%20Law%20School.%20The%20Delaware%20judge%20will%20scrutinize%20the%20vote%20and%20require%20Tesla%20to%20prove%20the%20process%20was%20not%20coerced%20or%20improperly%20influenced%20by%20Musk%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20had%20criticized%20Tesla's%20board%20as%20%26quot%3Bbeholden%26quot%3B%20to%20him%2C%20saying%20the%20plan%20was%20proposed%20by%20a%20conflicted%20board%20with%20close%20personal%20and%20financial%20ties%20to%20its%20top%20executive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20shareholders%20also%20approved%20a%20proposal%20to%20move%20the%20company's%20legal%20home%20to%20Texas%20from%20Delaware.%20They%20also%20approved%20other%20proposals%20including%20the%20re-election%20of%20two%20board%20members%3A%20Musk's%20brother%20Kimbal%20Musk%20and%20James%20Murdoch%2C%20son%20of%20media%20mogul%20Rupert%20Murdoch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShareholders%20did%20increase%20the%20level%20of%20investor%20control%20by%20passing%20proposals%20in%20favor%20of%20shortening%20board%20terms%20to%20one%20year%20and%20lowering%20voting%20requirements%20for%20proposals%20to%20a%20simple%20majority%2C%20despite%20board%20opposition%20to%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E'DEAL%20IS%20A%20DEAL'%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20on%20Thursday%20did%20not%20disclose%20the%20voting%20tallies%2C%20which%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20revealed%20in%20coming%20days.%20At%20least%20a%20half-million%20viewers%20watched%20the%20meeting%20on%20the%20livestream%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X%2C%20and%20about%2040%2C000%20watched%20on%20YouTube.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%2C%20firstly%2C%20a%20message%20that%20Tesla's%20retail%20shareholders%20do%20approve%20of%20what's%20going%20on.%20It%20will%20be%20interesting%20to%20see%20what%20the%20exact%20percentages%20of%20the%20votes%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lindsey%20Stewart%2C%20a%20director%20at%20Morningstar%20Sustainalytics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShareholder%20approval%20for%20the%20compensation%20serves%20as%20both%20an%20endorsement%20of%20Musk's%20tenure%20and%20an%20acknowledgment%20that%20investors%20do%20not%20want%20to%20risk%20the%20company's%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20brushing%20aside%20essentially%20key%20man%20risks%2C%20where%20Tesla%20has%20become%20even%20more%20dependent%20on%20Musk%20going%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jason%20Schloetzer%2C%20a%20business%20professor%20at%20Georgetown%20University%20with%20expertise%20in%20corporate%20governance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20Musk%20threatened%20to%20build%20AI%20and%20robotics%20products%20outside%20of%20Tesla%20if%20he%20failed%20to%20gain%20enough%20voting%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20shifted%20the%20company's%20focus%20to%20robotaxis%2C%20shelving%20cheaper%20mass-market%20electric%20cars%2C%20to%20the%20concern%20of%20some%20investors%20who%20feared%20the%20autonomous%20technology%20will%20be%20hard%20to%20perfect.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20update%20on%20Tesla's%20performance%2C%20Musk%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20company%20recently%20shipped%20a%20record%201%2C300%20Cybertrucks%20in%20a%20week%20and%20that%20plans%20for%20volume%20production%20of%20its%20Semi%20trucks%20were%20in%20place.%20He%20talked%20at%20length%20about%20plans%20for%20autonomous%20cars%2C%20though%20he%20gave%20no%20time%20frame%20for%20a%20launch%20of%20self-driving%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla's%20share%20price%20has%20dropped%20about%2055%25%20from%20its%202021%20peak%20as%20EV%20sales%20have%20slowed%20and%20Musk's%20attention%20has%20wavered%20between%20Tesla%20and%20other%20companies%20he%20runs.%20The%20stock%20closed%20up%202.9%25%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShareholders%20once%20again%20endorsed%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20contract%2C%20sending%20a%20strong%20signal%20that%20'a%20deal%20is%20a%20deal'%20and%20Musk%20deserves%20to%20be%20rewarded%20for%20meeting%20the%20lofty%20thresholds%20of%20an%20entirely%20incentive-based%20contract%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Garrett%20Nelson%2C%20analyst%20at%20CFRA%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20news%20lifts%20a%20major%20overhang%20on%20the%20shares%2C%20although%20we%20wouldn't%20be%20surprised%20by%20a%20%26quot%3Bsell%20the%20news%26quot%3B%20reaction%20on%20Friday%20following%20big%20gains%20over%20the%20past%20two%20trading%20sessions%20as%20the%20likely%20outcome%20became%20clearer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20board%20had%20said%20that%20Musk%20deserves%20the%20package%20because%20he%20hit%20all%20the%20ambitious%20targets%20on%20market%20value%2C%20revenue%20and%20profitability.%20Large%20investors%20including%20the%20California%20Public%20Employees'%20Retirement%20System%20had%20called%20the%20pay%20package%20%26quot%3Bexcessive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EPRESSURE%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElon%20Musk%20and%20Chair%20(Robyn)%20Denholm%20have%20made%20this%20about%20CEO%20loyalty%20and%20presented%20the%20votes%20as%20a%20decision%20about%20whether%20the%20company%20can%20keep%20Musk%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ivan%20Frishberg%2C%20chief%20sustainability%20office%20at%20Amalgamated%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20but%20it%20doesn't%20change%20the%20fact%20that%20good%20governance%20is%20good%20for%20the%20bottom%20line%20of%20a%20company%2C%20and%20the%20Tesla%20board%20is%20consistently%20and%20clearly%20deficient%20on%20that%20front.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Musk%20is%20undoubtedly%20Tesla's%20driving%20force%2C%20and%20is%20credited%20with%20much%20of%20its%20success%2C%20the%20company's%20sales%20and%20profit%20have%20slowed.%20There%20are%20concerns%20that%20he%20is%20spreading%20himself%20too%20thin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20added%20two%20more%20companies%20to%20his%20roster%20since%20the%20pay%20package%20was%20approved%20in%202018.%20He%20now%20runs%20or%20owns%20six%20firms%2C%20including%20rocket-builder%20SpaceX%2C%20social%20media%20giant%20X%20-%20formerly%20Twitter%20-%20and%20the%20artificial-intelligence%20firm%20xAI%2C%20which%20Musk%20created%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718335920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fdj5hfntg_elon-musk_625x300_14_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftesla-shareholders-approve-elon-musks-56-billion-pay-package-5881323%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tesla%20shareholders%20approved%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk's