%20event%20%26quot%3Bdeserve%20it%26quot%3B.%20Pakistan%20got%20a%20reprieve%20on%20Wednesday%20after%20arch-rivals%20India%20won%20the%20match%20against%20USA%20as%20this%20has%20kept%20up%20hopes%20of%20Azam-led%20team%20of%20making%20it%20to%20the%20next%20stage%20of%20the%20marquee%20event%20through%20the%20remaining%20spot%20from%20the%20group.%20India%20clinched%20a%20hard-fought%207-wicket%20win%20over%20the%20co-hosts%20USA.%20The%20victory%20took%20Rohit%20Sharma-led%20side%20to%20the%20Super-8%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20fate%20still%20hangs%20in%20the%20balance.%20The%20Men%20in%20Green%20need%20Ireland%20to%20do%20a%20favour%20to%20them%20by%20defeating%20the%20USA%20on%20Friday%2C%20which%20will%20take%20the%20qualification%20matter%20to%20net%20run%20rate.%20If%20the%20US%20prevail%20over%20Ireland%2C%20the%20Men%20in%20Green's%20campaign%20will%20conclude%20on%20a%20sour%20note%20though%20they%20will%20have%20one%20more%20match%20to%20play%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20luck%20favours%20Pakistan%20and%20they%20win%20over%20Ireland%20in%20their%20final%20game%20of%20the%20group%20stage%2C%20they%20could%20qualify%20to%20Super%208%20with%20a%20better%20NRR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Indian%20pacer%20feels%20it%20would%20be%20a%20miracle%20if%20Pakistan%20manage%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20next%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20Pakistan%20is%20following%20the%20needed%20routine.%20They%20don't%20focus%20on%20their%20domestic%20leagues.%20All%20of%20their%20legends%2C%20like%20Wasim%20bhai%20(Akram)%20and%20even%20Waqar%20Younis%2C%20say%20they%20need%20to%20change%20the%20entire%20system.%20So%20that%20says%20where%20they%20are%20going%20wrong.%20I%20will%20only%20say%20this%20to%20Pakistan%20all%20the%20best%20for%20the%20next%20World%20Cup.%20If%20they%20come%20back%20from%20this%20position%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20miracle.%20I%20don't%20think%20it%20will%20be%20easy%2C%26quot%3B%20Sreesanth%2C%20who%20features%20as%20an%20expert%20on%20'Caught%20and%20Bold'%20programme%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20supporters%20will%20be%20keenly%20following%20the%20play%20at%20Florida%20stadium%2C%20where%20USA%20will%20take%20on%20Ireland.%20USA%20have%20won%20two%20of%20their%20three%20games%20-%20against%20Pakistan%20and%20Canada%20-%20displaying%20discipline%2C%20sharpness%20and%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20India%20won%20the%20match%2C%20USA%20team%20put%20up%20a%20strong%20fight.%20Shivam%20Dube%20and%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20held%20their%20composure%20to%20see%20off%20the%20game%20for%20the%20Men%20in%20Blue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUSA%20Captain%20Monank%20Patel%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20Saurabh%20Nethralvakar%20and%20many%20other%20stars%20have%20left%20their%20mark%20on%20the%20field%20with%20some%20eye-catching%20performances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESreesanth%20feels%20that%20the%20co-hosts%20deserve%20to%20go%20into%20the%20next%20round%20and%20face%20the%20top%20sides%20to%20continue%20their%20fairytale%20story%20in%20the%20marquee%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20things%20about%20T20%20World%20Cup%20is%20every%20team%20looks%20strong%20on%20paper.%20If%20we%20talk%20about%20planning%20and%20execution%2C%20the%20USA%20team%20prevailed%20because%20of%20their%20planning%20and%20execution%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years%20and%20they%20have%20worked%20hard.%20I%20want%20the%20USA%20team%20to%20play%20in%20the%20Top%208%20because%20they%20deserve%20it.%20They%20have%20done%20more%20than%20enough%20justice%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Top%208%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20will%20conclude%20their%20group%20stage%20on%20Sunday%20against%20Ireland%20at%20Florida.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718334300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F869eg61_india-pakistan-t20-wc_625x300_10_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2