o%20improvise.%20I%20remember%20on%20set%2C%20he%20always%20wore%20the%20same%20thing%3A%20jeans%2C%20a%20vest%2C%20and%20a%20lengthy%20jacket.%20He%20looked%20like%20a%20conductor.%20He%20had%20a%20uniform%2C%20it%20seemed.%20He%20was%20kind%20of%20like%20a%20pied%20piper%20because%2C%20with%20every%20shot%2C%20there%20would%20be%20a%20trail%20of%20four%20or%20five%20people%20behind%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20heard%20you%20and%20Robert%20Downey%20Jr.%20developing%20something%20together.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are.%20I%20can%20tell%20you%20that%20we%20are%20in%20development%3B%20it's%20been%20years.%20We%20wrote%20a%20TV%20series%20together%2C%20we're%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3BSingularity%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20it's%20based%20on%20an%20idea%20Downey%20had.%20It's%20taken%20a%20while%20because%2C%20at%20a%20certain%20point%2C%20we%20had%20to%20change%20things%20because%20it%20wound%20up%20being%20too%20similar%20to%20%26quot%3BSuccession.%26quot%3B%20What%20I%20mean%20by%20that%20is%20I%20would%20have%20played%20one%20of%20three%20sons%2C%20and%20the%20father%20was%20this%20tycoon%20industrialist.%20It's%20more%20of%20a%20comedic%20tone%20than%20%26quot%3BSuccession%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20it%20mirrored%20it%20too%20much%2C%20so%20we%20had%20to%20change%20things.%20Downey%20and%20I%20actually%20had%20a%20Zoom%20session%20the%20other%20day%20with%20a%20top%20producer%20who%20will%20hopefully%20come%20on%20board.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWould%20Downey%20be%20on%20camera%20alongside%20you%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20willing%20to%20do%20that.%20He%20might%20direct%20the%20pilot%20and%20some%20other%20episodes%20along%20with%20being%20in%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWould%20you%20direct%20some%20episodes%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20love%20to.%20This%20is%20really%20Downey's%20idea%2C%20so%20he's%20committed%20to%20being%20a%20part%20of%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou've%20had%20s