gn%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Muneeb%20Amin%20Bhat%20(%40bhatmuneeb_)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20inform%20my%20friends%20to%20secure%20their%20social%20media%20accounts.%20When%20I%20informed%20the%20shop%20owners%20or%20neighbours%20about%20the%20security%20leak%20in%20their%20Wi-Fi%2C%20they%20would%20appreciate%20my%20efforts%20and%20thank%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Muneeb%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20understanding%20the%20importance%20of%20his%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20the%20go-to%20%E2%80%98gadget%20fixer%E2%80%99%20in%20his%20village%20for%20any%20problems%20in%20mobile%20phones%20and%20computers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20living%20in%20a%20village%20which%20lacked%20facilities%20and%20faced%20challenges%20ranging%20from%20electricity%20to%20internet%20connectivity%2C%20he%20pursued%20his%20passion%20in%20the%20era%20of%202g%20cellular%20network.%20Watching%20movies%20like%20The%20Matrix%2C%20Live%20Free%20or%20Die%20Hard%2C%20opened%20his%20eyes%20to%20the%20world%20of%20ethical%20hacking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20father%20bought%20their%20first%20computer%20in%202012%2C%20post%20which%2C%20the%20young%20boy%20would%20spend%20hours%20on%20the%20internet%20learning%20the%20basics%20of%20hardware%2C%20networking%20and%20programming.%20He%20learnt%20from%20tutorials%20on%20Google%20and%20YouTube%2C%20following%20the%20likes%20of%20the%20late%20Kevin%20Mitnick%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20famous%20hackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20that%20we%20can%20secure%20data%20for%20organisations.%20Even%20though%20companies%20have%20their%20own%20security%20teams%2C%20they%20invite%20ethical%20hackers%20to%20report%20vulnerabilities%20in%20their%20data%20through%20their%20responsible%20disclosure%20programme%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20343%20million%20people%20have%20been%20th