ersecurity-data-breach-bug-bounty-india-kashmir%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Grow%20a%20Vertical%20Vegetable%20Garden%20Using%20PVC%20Pipes%20On%20Your%20Terrace%20%26amp%3B%20Balcony%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOften%20those%20living%20in%20metropolitan%20cities%20hesitate%20to%20garden%20at%20home%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20space.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303431%2Fup-man-shows-how-to-grow-organic-vegetables-in-pvc-pipes-farming-startup-veg-roof%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMithilesh%20Kumar%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Sunita%20Prasad%20from%20Bihar%2C%20have%20defied%20this%20notion%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20urban%20areas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Mithilesh%20has%20successfully%20cultivated%20a%20variety%20of%20crops%20including%20chilli%2C%20coriander%2C%20tomato%2C%20brinjal%2C%20okra%2C%20peas%2C%20and%20bitter%20gourd%20in%20his%20compact%20garden%2C%20Sunita%20has%20also%20found%20similar%20success%20in%20her%20home%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20secret%3F%20Vertical%20gardening%20using%20PVC%20pipes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunita%20has%20installed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F284723%2Fvertical-garden-pvc-pipes-bamboo-organic-vegetables-how-to-terrace-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPVC%20pipes%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20create%20a%20vertical%20garden%20where%20she%20grows%20around%205%20kg%20of%20vegetables%20every%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Mithilesh%20says%20that%20using%20PVC%20pipes%20saves%20space%20as%20well%20as%20money.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20general%2C%20PVC%20pipes%20are%20cheap%2C%20easy%20to%20find%2C%20and%20can%20save%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20space.%20Moreover%2C%20it%20does%20not%20require%20a%20complicated%20set%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C